@article.set_section "Provide more information about a tender", <<-SECTION_6

<p>Include in your response:</p>
<ul>
  <li>the submission deadline</li>
  <li>the language the bid must be submitted in</li>
  <li>further details about the tender such as the reference number, registration process or any costs attached to bidding</li>
  <li>the tender documents as a link or attachment</li>
  <li>how you could help them further if possible such as directing them to legal advice, translation or other services</li>
</ul>

<p>Use sentences such as:
